% Harry Potter's room of potions logical puzzle:

| ?- potions::potions(P1, P2, P3, P4, P5, P6, P7).

P1 = poison
P2 = wine
P3 = forward
P4 = poison
P5 = poison
P6 = wine
P7 = backwards

yes
